arts.ttl: Arsenal vs Leeds United: Pre-match analysis
arts.sum: Leeds United showed the whole of the Championship last season that their attacking football was good enough to compete and helped them win the league. Depending on the full backs that start the game for Mikel Arteta's side, Riccardo Calafiori and Ben White like to attack high and wide leaving space for the Leeds United wingers.

arts.ttl: Report: Bukayo Saka spotted playing in a different position during Arsenal training ahead of Leeds clash
